I didn't mention in my prepared remarks, but we've taken $1.4 billion of debt out at the completion of this tender over the last 3.5 years. And as I did say, we're going to, at a net debt-to-EBITDA ratio, we'll end this year approximately 3 times. So, we think we've made substantial improvement to our capital structure. And we're going to continue to look for ways to improve it as we move forward.

