Individual




Marvin R. Ellison



Mr. Marvin R. Ellison is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at J. C. Penney Co., Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Retail Industry Leaders Association, FedEx Corp., US Home Systems, Inc. and Atlanta Police Foundation. Mr. Ellison was previously employed as an Independent Director by H&R Block, Inc., Executive Vice President-US Stores by The Home Depot, Inc., and Director-Assets Protection by Target Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Memphis and an MBA from Emory University.



